{"tid":2160106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新冠病毒可能最早出現在2012年","createTime":"2020-08-16T17:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T18:03:08.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b33995bb2b309dcc7f8b3194736257cd21136652","tid":2160106,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:58:27.000Z","msg":"有美國研究人員指出，被廣泛認為是去年底從武漢開始蔓延的新冠病毒，可能最早起源於2012年。<br />\n<br />\n據《紐約郵報》的報導，紐約一家非盈利生物科技研究機構的研究人員早前曾指出，根據名為李旭（音譯Li Xu）的醫生的碩士學位論文，2012年4月，雲南墨江一處礦藏的6名礦工在打掃蝙蝠排泄物後，感染了類似新冠的病毒，其中有3人後來死亡。<br />\n<br />\n這名醫生當時診治這6位礦工的方法與目前診治新冠病人的方法相似，當時他還遠程問診中國工程院院士鐘南山。<br />\n<br />\n李旭後來又將病毒樣本寄給了武漢病毒研究所。紐約這家研究機構的科研人員相信，這些早期的病毒後來進化成如今的新冠病毒。這種說法在美國科學界正獲得越來越多的支持。<br />\n<br />\n這家科研機構的科研人員還認為，新冠病毒很大概率就是從武漢病毒研究所洩露出來的。<br />\n<br />\n英國媒體《星期日泰晤士報》7月份也報導過雲南可能是新冠病毒最早起源地。<br />\n<br />\n（責編：王允）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/3-08162020104918.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2FXinwen%2F3-08162020104918.html&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=d4d18d7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/3-08162020104918.html</a>"},{"pid":"b6f07c825ac62f31138a33edde290b4fb832d7fc","tid":2160106,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"COVID-19 first appeared in a group of Chinese miners in 2012, scientists say<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2020/08/15/covid-19-first-appeared-in-chinese-miners-in-2012-scientists/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2020%2F08%2F15%2Fcovid-19-first-appeared-in-chinese-miners-in-2012-scientists%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=6c6a88a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2020/08/15/covid-19-first-appeared-in-chinese-miners-in-2012-scientists/</a>"},{"pid":"9c752efed6875a4590e2c6955dbe73d10268d388","tid":2160106,"uid":185892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T18:00:19.000Z","msg":"雲南肺炎"},{"pid":"330d73a98a84e5dda94ec95ac76975b18307420d","tid":2160106,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T18:01:09.000Z","msg":"點解至今無見學者quote過閻麗夢啲野"},{"pid":"4957a93f6864dd53a0324d136936a1b4ced2e63e","tid":2160106,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T18:03:08.000Z","msg":"即係野生再變人工跟住爆<br />\n但咁樣好容易俾支共spin去純天然"}]}